          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Changes: Refactored OAuth login/registration flow to use ExternalIdentity.ExternalId as the primary identifier instead of email/username lookup. "
            }
          ],
          "attrs": {
            "localId": "af9eabf19258"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "What was done:                 "
            }
          ],
          "attrs": {
            "localId": "af9eabf19258"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "orderedList",
          "attrs": {
            "order": 1,
            "localId": "28828019c817"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "attrs": {
                "localId": "3efa2d5e5c65"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "BaseOAuthAccountService - Added tiered identity resolution: first looks up user by ExternalId in ExternalIdentity table (stable identifier), falls back to email/username lookup for pre-migration users. Backfills ExternalId on successful login for older accounts.  "
                    }
                  ],
                  "attrs": {
                    "localId": "af9eabf19258"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "attrs": {
                "localId": "3fe96d4233db"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " GoogleAccountService - Uses email as ExternalId. OneTap flows pass externalId through."
                    }
                  ],
                  "attrs": {
                    "localId": "af9eabf19258"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "attrs": {
                "localId": "3fe96d4233db"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "TelegramAccountService - Uses TG{telegramUserId} as ExternalId. "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "hardBreak"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Tier 1: ExternalIdentity lookup \u2192 Tier 2: UserName fallback \u2192 Tier 3: Register. "
                    }
                  ],
                  "attrs": {
                    "localId": "af9eabf19258"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "attrs": {
                "localId": "c97f1f77f0b2"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Backfill migration - Populates ExternalId for existing users:"
                    }
                  ],
                  "attrs": {
                    "localId": "af9eabf19258"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "orderedList",
                  "attrs": {
                    "order": 1,
                    "localId": "b6d6930a5ed1"
                  },
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "attrs": {
                        "localId": "c97f1f77f0b2"
                      },
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Telegram: copies UserName (TG-prefixed) to ExternalId, inserts missing ExternalIdentity rows for orphan clients"
                            }
                          ],
                          "attrs": {
                            "localId": "af9eabf19258"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "attrs": {
                        "localId": "c97f1f77f0b2"
                      },
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Google: copies lowercased Email to ExternalId"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "hardBreak"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Adds composite index on (ExternalId, RegistrationSourceId)"
                            }
                          ],
                          "attrs": {
                            "localId": "af9eabf19258"
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Impact: Login resolves by stable external identifier first, with transparent fallback for pre-migration users."
            }
          ],
          "attrs": {
            "localId": "25d8d5ac978d"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "How to test:"
            }
          ],
          "attrs": {
            "localId": "0a600bb94fc1"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "attrs": {
                "localId": "1b12612e9bcd"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Google login: existing user logs in \u2192 verify login succeeds, ExternalId gets backfilled in ExternalIdentity table"
                    }
                  ],
                  "attrs": {
                    "localId": "9f2eef0539fe"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
